    "label": "Conflict within one principle",
    "explanation": "Given that you should promote others’ wellbeing, the two strangers being in danger is a reason to save them. Given that you should promote others’ wellbeing, the one stranger being in danger is a reason to save her. Because saving more people provides more wellbeing, the reason to save the two strangers is stronger."
